name: Nursing Necklace #5
description:
Black and red fair trade, handmade beads from Indonesia.  Always non toxic and made with a breakaway clasp, safe for baby and mama. Perfect for occupying little hands during nursing, bottle feeding, diaper changing, baby wearing, playing, snuggling, buggy rides and so so much more!

Due to the handmade nature of our beads and the knotting technique we use, necklaces vary in length.
